About Miami
***********

   Miami is a TCP/IP stack including PPP and (C)SLIP and is compatible
to AmiTCP. Miami is programmed and maintained by Holger Kruse.

   You can get the public releases of Miami from Aminet, for the latest
beta releases take a look at the Miami homepage.

Holger Kruse's email address: @{b}kruse@nordicglobal.com@{ub}
Miami homepage: @{b}http://www.nordicglobal.com/Miami.html@{ub}


@EndNode

